      "para_id": "Q001836.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Šu-Suen , the beloved of Enlil , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Dada , governor of Nibru , child of Ur-Nanibgal , governor of Nibru , is your servant ."
